(Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figure 4. Epeolus leleji sp. nov., paratype, female A, B habitus, lateral view (A); dorsal view (B) C head, frontal view D apex of metasoma, ventral view. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A, B); 0.5 mm (C, D)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.67150.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/578842" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">4</figureCitation>
